Bubo Defense team,

Army Systems Command is issuing RFP-2026-0512 for an upgrade to our
tactical ISR sensor-fusion stack. This work is squarely in the secure
sensor-integration domain and is available under the SEWP V contract
vehicle, which Bubo Defense holds.

Estimated value is $4.1M over 24 months. Proposals are due in 30 days
(by June 11, 2026). Your team delivered the FY24 prototype for this
program, so you have clear incumbency.

Please confirm intent to bid.

Regards,
